Subject: [PATCH] fix(news): expand semantic-graph TOKEN_TO_NODE with Indian
 PSU + DC + nuclear + defense + fab patterns (0098)
MIME-Version: 1.0
Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit

Closes the gap where 66% of Indian articles fired graph_primary_node = NONE.
Diagnostic on live API showed:
  TOTAL India-region: 39 articles
  PRIMARY_NODES: NONE = 26 (66%) · ENERGY_INFRA = 5 · MEMORY = 2 ·
                 FAB = 2 · OIL/GAS = 2 · RENEWABLE = 2
  Examples missed: NTPC nuclear feasibility study, HAL LCA Mk1A delivery,
  HAL Sidelined for AMCA Stealth Jet, Hyundai India Rs 7,500 Cr capex.

ADDED ~30 Indian-specific regex patterns to TOKEN_TO_NODE.  Pure regex,
NO hardcoded ticker→bottleneck dictionaries (the user explicitly asked
not to hardcode).

COMPUTE_INFRA — Indian DC operators + IndiaAI Mission
  Yotta / ESDS / CtrlS / NxtGen / Sify / Adani Connex / Hiranandani DC /
  Reliance Jio cloud / Airtel cloud / Web Werks
  IndiaAI Mission / sovereign AI / GPU cluster India / hyperscaler India
  '\d+ MW DC' phrasing

ENERGY_INFRA — Indian PSU power + transmission EPC
  NTPC / Power Grid / Tata Power / Adani Power+Transmission+Green / NHPC /
  NLC India / SJVN / JSW Energy / NTPC Green
  KEC International / Sterlite Power / Tata Projects / L&T T&D / CG Power
  ABB India / Siemens India / Hitachi Energy India
  REC / PFC / IREDA / IEX

NUCLEAR_INFRA — broader India (DAE, NTPC nuclear, BARC, BHAVINI)
  Department of Atomic Energy + AERB + IGCAR + BARC + Bhabha Atomic
  NTPC nuclear feasibility / project / approval / nod
  Kakrapar / Tarapur / Kaiga / Narora / Rawatbhata / Gorakhpur nuclear
  PFBR / AHWR / HALEU India / Bharat SMR

FABRICATION_INFRA — India semicon mission + Tata + Vedanta-Foxconn
  India Semiconductor Mission / SemiconIndia / SEM 2.0
  Tata Electronics+Semiconductor / CG Power semiconductor / Tower India /
  Powerchip India / Kaynes Semicon
  'fab in Gujarat/Dholera/Sanand/Assam/Jagiroad' / Micron Sanand
  Vedanta-Foxconn

PACKAGING_INFRA — Indian OSAT
  Kaynes Semicon/OSAT / Tata OSAT/assembly / Micron assembly / ATMP India

INTERCONNECT_INFRA — Indian fibre
  Sterlite Tech / HFCL / Tejas Networks / Polycab / KEI / Finolex Cables

NETWORK_BANDWIDTH — Indian 5G + carrier edge + cable landings
  Jio/Airtel/Bharti 5G+fibre+xstream / India 5G+6G rollout / spectrum auction
  Chennai+Mumbai cable landing / 2Africa / SeaMeWe / NIXI / IX India
  BharatNet / FTTH

COOLING_INFRA — Indian DC cooling
  Voltas / Blue Star / Amber / EPACK / Symphony / Crompton / JCI India
  (companion DC/hyperscaler/HVAC)

RENEWABLE_INFRA — Indian RE + SECI tenders
  ReNew / Adani Green / Suzlon / Inox Wind / Greenko / NTPC Green /
  JSW Renew / Borosil Renewables / Premier Energies / Waaree
  SECI tender/allocation/PPA/auction / solar park India / wind-solar hybrid

DEFENSE_INFRA — Indian defence PSUs + platforms (NO companion req)
  HAL / BEL / BDL / Mazagon Dock / Cochin Shipyard / GRSE / MIDHANI / BEML / DRDO
  AMCA / TEDBF / Su-30 MKI / Tejas Mk / Prachand / Dhruv / Astra/Nag/Akash NG /
  QRSAM / SMARKA / Spike / NASAMS / ATAGS / Nirbhay / Shaurya / Prithvi
  MoD clears / CCS clears / AON / Acceptance of Necessity

AEROSPACE_INFRA — Indian space
  ISRO / NSIL / IN-SPACe / Skyroot / Agnikul / Pixxel / Bellatrix /
  Dhruva Space / Paras Defence
  SSLV / Chandrayaan / Gaganyaan / Aditya-L1 / NavIC / GSAT / RISAT / Cartosat

MANUFACTURING_CAPACITY — Indian capex / PLI / EMS
  'Rs X crore capex' / '₹ X crore' (with capex companion)
  Make in India / Atmanirbhar / China + One / EMS
  Dixon / Amber / Kaynes / Syrma SGS / Cyient DLM / EPACK / Elin / Optiemus

RESOURCE_SCARCITY — Indian critical minerals
  IREL / NMDC / MOIL / HZL / KABIL / GMDC / NALCO
  Critical Mineral Mission India / China export ban India / India rare earth

LOGISTICS_INFRA — Indian ports + corridors
  Adani Ports / JNPT / Mumbai/Chennai/Paradip/Kandla/Mundra/Tuticorin/
  Vizhinjam/Vadhavan/Deendayal/Krishnapatnam/Gangavaram
  DFC / Sagarmala / BharatMala / Gati Shakti / MMLP

CAPITAL_CONSTRAINT — Indian banking + fund-raising
  RBI MPC / NBFC capital / IND-AS 109 / CRAR / LCR
  QIP / Rights issue / Preferential allotment

Cache key bumped v34 → v35. Articles will reclassify on next pull.
